data.description: Find this charming 2-Story Traditional Home in Blue Ridge, ready for you to claim as yours in 2024! Discover the epitome of Southern living in this charming home. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 2 half baths, this residence offers a perfect blend of classic elegance and modern comfort. Enjoy the warmth of wood floors throughout, (no carpet) a oversized gourmet kitchen, separate dining room comfortable for a 8-10 person table top, and a master suite retreat. The finished basement provides versatile space, while the open yard, partial fencing, greenhouse, and storage building enhance the outdoor experience. Notable features include a new roof with a 50-year warranty (installed 2022), micro mesh gutter guards, a three-year-old water heater, and a two-car garage. Embrace a private oasis with fresh paint throughout, making this home a true haven in the heart of Blue Ridge. Call to TOUR TODAY!
